He kissed me, you all kissed me, alright?

00:06:55.667 --> 00:06:58.133
This one didn’t ? Alright.

00:06:58.300 --> 00:07:03.434
Thank you, thank you very much, may God bless you all.

00:07:06.467 --> 00:07:13.734
Now, we are facing little children.

00:07:14.367 --> 00:07:22.033
They are the ones who are incarnations.

00:07:23.801 --> 00:07:29.725
